data.description: You will love living in this move in ready townhome settled on a private cul-de-sac in The Pines subdivision. It offers an updated kitchen with newer appliances and quartz countertops. The large island expands to the spacious living area allowing for easy and comfortable entertainment. The laundry room is on the main level along with a half bath.  HVAC and water heater were replaced in 2019.  The upstairs includes a loft space that can be used as toy/game room or office space.  The Master bedroom offers an additional living space along with it's own private vanity and walk in closet. Enjoy the private patio and 2 car garage. Conveniently located to major highways making commute a breeze. Welcome Home!
